{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_otter_set_2_story_1","storyGroup":"story_otter_set_2","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"造物之心","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"在“咪波智能升级”的事情上，梅尔始终坚持自研，她又失败了一次。可能还会有下一次，但那又怎么样呢？","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_otter_2_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["梅尔","可露希尔","咪波SUPER","？？？","咪波"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":5,"musicid":0},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_corridor","screenadapt":"coverall","id":6},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"Text","text":"罗德岛本舰","id":8},{"type":"Text","text":"“鲁特拉工作室”","id":9},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":10},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"要睁大眼睛看好哦，可露希尔。","id":11},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"......","id":13},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":14},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波SUPER，请从操作台上挑出M-11型源石隔离漆层。","id":15},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"（上面的抗源石涂料起码有十几种，去掉了包装，外形和质地都差不多。）","id":17},{"type":"Dialog","id":18},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":19},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":20},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"100","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":22},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-100","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":23},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":24},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$getcast","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":26},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"完全正确。","id":28},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"这只是基本能力啦。","id":30},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"这套热能感应装置里有个组件坏了，咪波SUPER，请在三分钟内修复它。","id":32},{"type":"Dialog","id":33},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":34},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":35},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$tokenset","volume":"0.5","id":36},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-10","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":37},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":38},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"10","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":39},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":40},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-10","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":41},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":42},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"10","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":43},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"已经修复完毕。另外，还检测到有个电子元件附在了基座下面，会影响热能感应的效率，现已取出，装置可以正常使用。","id":46},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"真棒！才花了两分钟不到。","id":48},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#5","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"哇！它会说话！","id":50},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"智能版本当然要加装语音模块嘛。","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"它刚开口的时候，我也很不适应就是了。不过它即使能说话，好像也不怎么爱说话。","id":53},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"为什么是这种粗粗的声线......算了不重要，我和梅尔的审美差距很大哦嘿嘿。","id":55},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"继续继续。","id":57},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":58},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波SUPER，请重新设置工作室的门禁密码。","id":59},{"type":"Dialog","id":60},{"type":"Character","id":61},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":62},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"150","fadetime":"1.2","block":"true","id":63},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":64},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$char_escape","volume":"0.5","id":65},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":66},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"已经重置，新密码采用了大小写字母、生僻符号、数字等共计五种字符的组合。对了，数字并不是你的生日。","id":67},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","fadetime":"0","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"呜哇，真厉害！","id":69},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我宣布，应用试验第一阶段，成功！","id":71},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#1","focus":"1","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"怎么样，咪波全新智能版本的原型机——咪波SUPER，表现如何？是不是比你的人工智能小车要厉害？","id":73},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#4","focus":"2","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"真是聪明的小伙！可是，刚刚这些，Lancet-2和Castle-3它们也能做到哦。","id":75},{"type":"Dialog","id":76},{"type":"Character","id":77},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"0.3","id":78},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":79},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"15","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":80},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.3","id":81},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":82},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"啊啊啊松口松口，怎么跟梅尔一样咬人呢！","id":84},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波SUPER，先放过她。","id":86},{"type":"Dialog","id":87},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"性能表现是否超过小车尚待评估，但确实比它们要记仇。","id":89},{"type":"Character","id":90},{"type":"Dialog","id":91},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":92},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"80","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":94},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","focus":"1","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":96},{"type":"Dialog","id":97},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":98},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":99},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"150","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":101},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","focus":"2","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"别过来，不许咬了！","id":103},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","fadetime":"0","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"梅尔，这次咪波SUPER升级，你花了多长时间？","id":105},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"嗯，我看看日程表......已经三个月了。","id":107},{"type":"dialog","id":108},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":111},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":112},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"1","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"2","amount":"0","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#1","focus":"1","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"可露希尔，可露希尔！你要的“雷神挑衅者熔岩猫魔鬼高性能作业平台”的优化方案我做好了，给你。","id":117},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#1","focus":"2","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"辛苦梅尔。接下来——","id":119},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"接下来的话，我想请假一个月。","id":121},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":122},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":123},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","power":"30","times":"1","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"哇！工作狂居然也会请假？是身体太累了？或者说......你是在暗示涨薪对不对？","id":125},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"当然不是。","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"目前莱茵生命和罗德岛的工作委托都结束了，日程表现在是清空的状态。","id":128},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"所以想要趁机升级一下咪波。","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":131},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"你不是一直在抽空升级咪波嘛，为什么突然要专门申请一段时间？","id":132},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"这几个月来，服役的咪波又报废了三只，还有几只待维修。","id":134},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"最初代的咪波......只剩下一只了。","id":136},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"呜呜呜，可怜的咪波。","id":138},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"虽然咪波的作业效率已经得到了提升，但遇到特别复杂的环境，或者执行精密度要求比较高的任务时，回收率还是无法保证。","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"如果咪波能达到人工智能的高度，它们就可以在完成任务的同时保护好自己了。","id":141},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"那我也来帮忙！","id":143},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"......","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"还是不了吧。","id":146},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"为什么，我们不是刚一起帮艾沃娜成功改造了“正义骑士号”。","id":148},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"那是依托PRTS进行的客制化，连可露希尔都没有完全掌握小车们的代码与运算逻辑吧。","id":150},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我不希望对咪波进行客制化，从莱茵生命到罗德岛，它们的所有改造都是我自己做的......","id":152},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"有问题我会请教可露希尔的。","id":154},{"type":"Dialog","id":155},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"2","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"1","block":"true","id":156},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":158},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":160},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":161},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":162},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"之前就已经给咪波搭载了学习装置，但肯定算不上真正的“智能”，我需要重新做起。","id":164},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我尝试直接对原先的咪波核心进行优化，从而完善它的自律逻辑。哎，效果并不太理想。","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"所以我重写了咪波核心底层的代码......花了很多时间。","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"原计划咪波SUPER的原型机应该是五只，可以进行对照实验，但最终才完成了一只。","id":168},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":170},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"但是！这只咪波SUPER，将是前所未有的！它可以应用于更多样更复杂的场景，爆破、勘探、测绘、侦查、作战以及日常生活。","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"更重要的是，它可以完全脱离我的操控，独立完成各种精密作业。","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"它将是全泰拉最厉害的智能机械......个头还小，量产起来也很方便，比可露希尔客制化的小车厉害多了。","id":174},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"到时候它们将组成一支真正的咪波大军！","id":176},{"type":"Dialog","id":177},{"type":"Character","id":178},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$tokenset","volume":"0.5","id":179},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.2","id":180},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"50","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":181},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-50","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":182},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"7","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"10","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":184},{"type":"Dialog","id":185},{"type":"Character","id":186},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":187},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":188},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"70","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":189},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":190},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-70","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":191},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"......","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"咪波SUPER身上这是？","id":194},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"铭牌啊，每一只咪波都有的。","id":196},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"问题是，它身上为什么会有这么多块！我看一下，C00-1、B03-4、B12、G70......","id":198},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"是以前那些无法再服役，或者彻底报废的咪波的铭牌。","id":200},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"我知道，但那些你不都镶进“大咪波碑”里了吗？你把它们都......","id":202},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"所以咪波SUPER是......“带着兄弟们的希望”，这样的意思吗？","id":204},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"嘿嘿。","id":206},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"不过，刚刚梅尔并没有关闭自己对咪波核心的控制权限吧。","id":208},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"嗯。","id":210},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"这样不能算达到了“智能”哦。","id":212},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":213},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"过两天会进行应用试验的下一阶段。","id":214},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":215},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"那我到时候再过来。","id":216},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"对了梅尔，下次试验之前，记得调整下咪波SUPER爆破程序的参数哦，这里可是罗德岛本舰，万一咪波SUPER......","id":218},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我得赶紧把今天的数据记录进试验日志里。","id":220},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","focus":"2","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"梅尔，你有没有在听我说话？","id":222},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","name2":"char_007_closre_1#6","focus":"1","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"知道了知道了。","id":224},{"type":"Dialog","id":225},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1","id":226},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":227},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorclosequite","id":228},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":229},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","fadetime":"0","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"对了咪波SUPER，你改的门禁新密码是多少啊，我试一下。","id":231},{"type":"playsound","key":"$getcast","volume":"0.5","id":232},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":234},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"......","id":236},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咦，奇怪，好像不对欸。","id":238},{"type":"dialog","id":239},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":240},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":241},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","id":243},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波SUPER！","id":244},{"type":"dialog","id":245},{"type":"Character","id":246},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":247},{"type":"playsound","key":"$tokenset","volume":"0.5","id":248},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"10","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":249},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":250},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":251},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","id":252},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"《咪波SUPER试验日志07》","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":253},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"今天要继续进行咪波全新智能版本原型机——咪波SUPER的应用试验。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":254},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我将暂时关闭对咪波核心的控制权限，让咪波SUPER自主对周围部分建筑进行检测及隐患排除作业。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":255},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"这是最最重要的阶段。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":256},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"这段时间以来，咪波会说话了，虽然我和它都有点不太习惯。它可以完成更为复杂的作业，不再是之前“长腿的炸弹”。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":257},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"但这是自有咪波以来，经历各个版本的迭代，它第一次完全脱离我的操控。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":258},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"如果成功，就意味着咪波真正达到了人工智能的高度，且并未依靠罗德岛中枢。这对鲁特拉工作室和咪波来说，都非常非常重要。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":259},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":260},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"虽然，有个别数据存在偏差，但就咪波SUPER之前的整体表现来看，我对今天试验的结果还是充满期待的，哈哈。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":261},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"毕竟，那么多只咪波，都在给我们力量呢。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":262},{"type":"Dialog","id":263},{"type":"subtitle","id":264},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":265},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":266},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":267},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波核心控制权限已关闭。","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波SUPER，接下来请对指定区域的建筑进行检测及隐患排除作业。","id":269},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":270},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"当然了，这里可是罗德岛本舰，你要......","id":271},{"type":"playsound","key":"$tokenset","volume":"0.5","id":272},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":273},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":274},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","id":275},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"嗨呀，你已经是智能咪波了，这点判断能力肯定是有的哈哈。","id":276},{"type":"Dialog","id":277},{"type":"Character","id":278},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":279},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":280},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"200","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":281},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":282},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":283},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$doorclosequite","volume":"1","id":284},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":285},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"呼——","id":287},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"接下来只需要等待咪波SUPER完成任务回来就行啦。","id":288},{"type":"Dialog","id":289},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":290},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"100","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":291},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":292},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","id":293},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":294},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":295},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"啊，新的工作委托，已经堆了这么多......看来这次确实耽搁了太久。","id":296},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":297},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我看看——唔，为部分干员宿舍加装墙体投影、训练场武器系统的调整升级、本舰无人机群和充能装置的联动方案......","id":298},{"type":"Dialog","id":299},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-100","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":300},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":301},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":302},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"呀，工作室里也乱糟糟的。","id":303},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"趁这个时间，收拾下操作台吧。","id":305},{"type":"Dialog","id":306},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":307},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.7","id":308},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"50","fadetime":"0.4","block":"true","id":309},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":310},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-50","fadetime":"0.4","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":312},{"type":"dialog","id":313},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":314},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":315},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":316},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":317},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$tokenset","volume":"0.5","delay":"0.2","id":318},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":319},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":320},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"咪波——SUPER。建筑检测。隐患排除。建筑检测。隐患排除。","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"共检测出八处不合理构造，计算量——隐患均已排除，方式为——","id":322},{"type":"Dialog","id":323},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","id":324},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"SoundVolume","volume":"1","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"0","id":326},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":327},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"0","id":328},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"还剩下最后一处。","id":329},{"type":"Character","id":330},{"type":"Text","text":"“鲁特拉工作室”","id":331},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","id":332},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"操作台这下看着整洁多啦！","id":333},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":334},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"Sound_Beta_2/Battle/b_char/b_char_botready","id":335},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"全景扫描。","id":337},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"调取比对数据——启用分析系统。","id":338},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"结果判定——","id":339},{"type":"Dialog","id":340},{"type":"MusicVolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"2","id":341},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"该空间建筑面积大于常规，生活或工作用途不明，存在危险器械——","id":344},{"type":"playsound","key":"$alarmenter","volume":"0.5","id":345},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"警告，隐患排除，请撤离。","id":346},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":347},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"接下来，把这几套热能感应装置修好。","id":348},{"type":"playsound","key":"$alarmenter","volume":"0.5","id":349},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":350},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"警告，隐患排除，请撤离。","id":351},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"原料又不太够了，看来明天得向采购部提交一批加购订单才行......","id":353},{"type":"playsound","key":"$alarmenter","volume":"0.5","id":354},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":355},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"隐患排除方式为——隐患排除方式为——为——","id":356},{"type":"StopMusic","fadetime":"2","id":357},{"type":"Dialog","id":358},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","xpos":"15","power":"0","times":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":359},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":360},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","xpos":"-15","power":"0","times":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":361},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":362},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","xpos":"15","power":"0","times":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":364},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","xpos":"-15","power":"0","times":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":365},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":366},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"爆破。","id":367},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":368},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"好像有什么动静......","id":369},{"type":"Dialog","id":370},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":371},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0.6","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":372},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":373},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$char_emp","volume":"0.5","id":374},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":375},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_surfacefrozen","id":376},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rockfall","delay":"0.5","id":377},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":378},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.3","id":379},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":380},{"type":"Text","text":"梅尔的反应并不算慢。当然，如果她没戴着耳机的话，还能更快一些。真是个坏习惯。","id":381},{"type":"Text","text":"咪波SUPER的爆破程序已经启动。","id":382},{"type":"Text","text":"延展式机械臂让梅尔及时按下了防冲击系统的启动按钮，这让咪波SUPER的定向爆破产生了偏差。","id":383},{"type":"Text","text":"鲁特拉工作室的主要区域并未受到影响，但门口承装工程材料的伸出式平台被击毁了。","id":384},{"type":"Text","text":"梅尔看着咪波SUPER被埋在了自己爆破炸出的废墟里。","id":385},{"type":"Dialog","id":386},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":387},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_doorbreak","volume":"0.5","id":388},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":389},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":390},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":391},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"呜哇！","id":392},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"$distressed_loop","volume":"0.4","id":393,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":394},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"啊，这些仪器怎么这么重！幸亏机械臂的充能装置没有受影响，不然都挪不开。","id":395},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":396},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波SUPER！","id":397},{"type":"Character","id":398},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$tokenset","volume":"0.3","id":399},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":400},{"type":"Dialog","id":401},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":402},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":403},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"梅尔，怎么回事，好远就听见你工作室的动静。","id":404},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":405},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"咪波SUPER......好像损毁得很严重。","id":406},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":407},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":408},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":409},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"这些，都是它干的吗？","id":410},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"也不能全怪它......早就跟你说不要将宿舍用作工作室，更不要扩建。我看看承重结构有没有......","id":411},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":412},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"......","id":413},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"对了，可露希尔，咪波SUPER不会在巡视的其他地方也......","id":414},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":415},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"我刚从那边过来，还好还好。","id":416},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":417},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"（幸亏留了个心眼，提前在附近加装了局域防冲击装置，呼——）","id":418},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":419},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"梅尔，你还好吗？","id":420},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"我帮你一起收拾吧。你看，都乱成这样了。","id":421},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":422},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"和那时候好像啊。","id":423},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":424},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"嗯？","id":425},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":426},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"唔，工作室这个乱糟糟的样子，和那时候好像。","id":427},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":428},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"呜呜你别吓我啊，怎么开始胡言乱语了呢，我不记得你是那种动不动就回忆的人啊。","id":429},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":430},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我是说最开始做咪波的时候......","id":431},{"type":"dialog","id":432},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":433},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":434},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"梅尔的工作室怎么又出问题了？","id":435},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这是本月第三回了吧。","id":436},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"要么是计时仪器突然停止运作，要么是冷凝系统故障，这回是......椅子自己弹起来把操作台撞翻了？","id":437},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"总之是些不大不小的故障，让她不得不暂离项目岗位，赶回自己的工作室......","id":438},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"都已经同意她成立一人工作室了......","id":439},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"她说是巧合，你就当是巧合吧。这点小心思，连心机都算不上。","id":440},{"type":"Dialog","id":441},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_corridor","screenadapt":"coverall","id":442},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":443},{"type":"Text","text":"能够进入莱茵生命，我超级兴奋。","id":444},{"type":"Text","text":"不仅是哥伦比亚，放在整个泰拉，那也是研究者眼中的圣地。有设备有项目有厉害的前辈福利待遇还好！","id":445},{"type":"Text","text":"科学能决定泰拉的未来，是我们的共识。但对于科学，莱茵生命内部，尤其是各个主任之间，各有各的理解，各有各的追求，偏执得很。","id":446},{"type":"Text","text":"氛围变得很奇怪，明明都是很厉害的研究者，但聚在一起效率却莫名地低。就像一支全明星组成的球队，总是打不赢比赛。","id":447},{"type":"Text","text":"我在的工程科，主要为其他科室提供技术支持。上个月由能量科牵头的项目，筹备到一半，由于总辖反对，这个月就可能中止或取消。","id":448},{"type":"Text","text":"同样，出于“某些”考虑，防卫科也能叫停正在进行的项目。","id":449},{"type":"Text","text":"在莱茵生命的时候，总发生类似的事情。小职员们只能把设备装了拆，拆了装，调试又调试。","id":450},{"type":"Text","text":"还不如自己搞点研究呢，我是这样想的。","id":451},{"type":"Text","text":"所以我捣鼓出了个捣蛋鬼闹钟。它会在设定好的时段里，在工作室搞点小破坏，虽然不严重但又必须要我马上赶回来处理的那种。","id":452},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":453},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"这就是咪波的雏形。","id":454},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"后来我把它们改造成了更实用的操纵机械。“咪波”也是加上开机提示音时取的名字。","id":455},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":456},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"呃，所以梅尔每次都开开心心地回来收拾乱糟糟的房间？","id":457},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":458},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"是呀哈哈。那段时间，虽说在总部参与的项目并没有取得什么实质性的进展，但我自己研发了不少小东西。","id":459},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"后来给赫默帮忙的时候，有些装置得到她的推荐，在莱茵生命一直应用至今呢。","id":460},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","id":461},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"咪波是梅尔最喜欢的作品吧。","id":462},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":463},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"嗯啊，我一直希望它们成为最厉害的智能机械。","id":464},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"毕竟从莱茵生命到罗德岛，这些家伙一直都陪着我，它们是大功臣！","id":465},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":466},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"只是因为报废回收、版本升级......初代服役的咪波只剩下一只了。","id":467},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":468},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"咪波SUPER......","id":469},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":470},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"就是在仅剩的这只初代机的基础上完成的。","id":471},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":472},{"type":"Dialog","id":473},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":474},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","id":475},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"《咪波SUPER试验日志08》","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":476},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"内部感应节点失效，肢体组件大面积不可逆变形......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":477},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"最重要的是，咪波核心毁损89.7%，很难修复。还是在代码和算法逻辑上出了问题，看来门禁密码出错就是个先兆。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":478},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"在回到鲁特拉工作室之前，咪波SUPER仅在本舰独立作业一个小时，便已经存在计算量过载的情况了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":479},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"它把干员们放在宿舍门口的物品判定为不合理构造，直接来了个爆破......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":480},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"好蠢啊，一点都不智能。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":481},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"呜呜呜。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":482},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"判定：咪波全新智能版本原型机——咪波SUPER失去应用价值。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":483},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"工作室墙面受损、物品折耗......需要一笔不小的维修费用呢。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":484},{"type":"subtitle","id":485},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":486},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"结论：本次咪波升级失败。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":487},{"type":"subtitle","id":488},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":489},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","id":490},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"想让机械达到人工智能的高度，哪儿有那么简单。","id":491},{"type":"Dialog","id":492},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":493},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"不要失落啊梅尔！","id":494},{"type":"Dialog","id":495},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":496},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":497},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-80","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":498},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":499},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-20","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":500},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":501},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","fadetime":"0","id":502},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":503},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":504},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"梅尔梅尔！","id":505},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":506},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"怎么啦？","id":507},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":508},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"从智能的角度来说，咪波SUPER虽然没有成功，但是也不算完全失败哦。","id":509},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":510},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"你不用安慰我啦，可露希尔。","id":511},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","id":512},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"你看这些！","id":513},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":514},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"......","id":515},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"——咪波的铭牌。","id":516},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#1","id":517},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"是啊。咪波SUPER的肢体组件都已经被重物压得碎裂变形了，它身上的铭牌虽然全部掉落......可是却完好无损欸。","id":518},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"铭牌的材质总不会有咪波组件本身坚固吧？","id":519},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":520},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"......","id":521},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":522},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":523},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"呜哇！你是说，它在受到冲击前......","id":524},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":525},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"可能只是巧合，也可能，是“本能”啊什么的......","id":526},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#2$1","id":527},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波SUPER......","id":528},{"type":"Dialog","id":529},{"type":"Character","id":530},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":531},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":532},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","id":533},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":534},{"type":"SoundVolume","volume":"1","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"0","id":535},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":536},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"0","id":537},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"咪波SUPER","text":"——","id":538},{"type":"StopMusic","fadetime":"3","id":539},{"type":"character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","id":540},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"语音模块严重损毁，它已经没办法回答什么了。","id":541},{"type":"dialog","id":542},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":543},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":544},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":545},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":546},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g9_headquarter","screenadapt":"coverall","id":547},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"1","block":"true","id":548},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":549},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"2","amount":"0","block":"true","id":550},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#4$1","id":551},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$tech_intro","key":"$tech_loop","volume":"0.4","id":552,"musicid":2},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"干得漂亮！你没看见我请假走的时候那些家伙的表情哈哈。","id":553},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","id":554},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"不过下次得把你放得远一些才行，弄倒椅子就行了，破坏了实验器材总归还是要花时间修复。","id":555},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#1$1","id":556},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我是不是该给你取个名字啊......这样吧，待会儿给你随机设置个开机提示音，提示音什么样你就叫什么名字！","id":557},{"type":"playsound","key":"$tokenset","volume":"0.5","id":558},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":559},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"——","id":560},{"type":"dialog","id":561},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":562},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":563},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":564},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":565},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":566},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波，过来，我要重新设定下你爆破程序的参数。","id":567},{"type":"Dialog","id":568},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":569},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":570},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","xpos":"30","power":"20","times":"1","fadetime":"0.4","block":"true","id":571},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":572},{"type":"character","name":"avg_242_otter_1#3$1","fadetime":"0","id":573},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波，帮我调整一下机械臂的位置。","id":574},{"type":"Dialog","id":575},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_545_1#1$1","id":576},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":577},{"type"